data.description: Cul-De-Sac living with an ELITE sought-after floor plan-the Julian from Mungo!Downstairs features an open-flowing floor plan that is an entertainer's dream.  A kitchen with a pantry and a great-sized bar that opens to the family room, & formal living room with coiffured ceilings.  An organization room that has been transformed into a meditation room, or perfect for a crafting room, & screened porch with ceiling fan & speakers to enjoy a Lowcountry afternoon.Upstairs features a unique split staircase leading to the loft and additional generous-sized bedrooms on the left, or go up the right side leading directly to the main attraction-a REALLY spacious Master Bedroom that can easily accommodate a California King & more.   Separate shower & garden tub.  Fenced Backyard & Shed to convey.
